INSTALL
    make
    sudo make install

USE
    talk
        enter interactive shell, then you can use commands to use it
        commands that you can use:
            send ip msg                 # send msg to ip
            send ip `shell command`     # exec this shell command and send the result
            l                           # read the first msg of msg queue
            quit                        # exit interactive shell
        
    echo "abc" | talk ip
        talk can recive pipe input
        

